dct_title_s: Plan of the town and fortifications of Gibraltar, exactly taken on the spot in the year 1738
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. "For Mr. Tindal's Continuation of Mr. Rapin's History of England"--printed below title. Probably issued in: Rapin de Thoyras, Paul. The history of England, translated by N. Tindal. London, 1745. v. 4.
